numberofproducts) as (SELECT categoryid,
                             categoryname,
                             (SELECT count(1)
                       FROM   products as p
                       WHERE  p.categoryid = c.categoryid) as numberofproducts
                      FROM   categories as c)

productname, unitprice) as (SELECT productid,
                                   categoryid,
                                   productname,
                                   unitprice
                            FROM   products as p
                            WHERE  unitprice > 10.0)

(SELECT c.categoryname,
        c.numberofproducts,
        p.productname,
        p.unitprice
 FROM   product_over10 as p
     INNER JOIN product_cat as c
         ON p.categoryid = c.categoryid
 ORDER BY productname)
